- **CIDR Block:** {{ vpc_cidr }}
- **Environment:** {{ environment }}
- **Project:** {{ project }}
- **Owner:** {{ owner }}
- **NAT Gateway:** {{ "Enabled" if enable_nat_gateway else "Disabled" }}

## Subnets

- **Public Subnets:** {{ public_subnet_cidrs | join(', ') }}
